version_description: David Bowie - Slip Away (Live) - No Capo - Link https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FQrJE56oU7I.
Easy song for beginners to sing and play.
The others have missed some chord changes.
Chord voicings as Bowie played it, with a few optional additional chords such as the F6 riff in the verses. Backing vocal. Chord legend included.
This version uses a capo making it somewhat easier to play
Intermediate version with split chords, voicings and song info.
Adapted and easier version for a better understanding.
